## 6. DNA Strip Pattern (Diagonal Bars)

The "DNA Strip" visualization shows maintenance patterns as diagonal stripes:

```
Stripe width: 8-12px
Stripe angle: 45deg (diagonal, running bottom-left to top-right)
Colors:
  - Blue (#1976D2) for mechanical/planned
  - Orange (#FF9800) for electrical/scheduled
Spacing: 2px between stripes
Background: White or very light gray (#FAFAFA)
```

This pattern represents the cyclic nature of train maintenance schedules.

