## 7. Heatmap Specifications

### 7.1 Cell Rendering

```
Cell size: Variable based on zoom (min 4px, max 40px)
Border: 0.5px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.05) (subtle grid)
Color: Mapped from intensity value (0-1) to gradient
Hover: Slight scale up (1.05), tooltip appears
```

### 7.2 Intensity Mapping

```typescript
// Map maintenance hours to color intensity
function getIntensity(hours: number, capacity: number): number {
  const ratio = hours / capacity;
  // Non-linear mapping for better visual differentiation
  return Math.min(1, Math.pow(ratio, 0.8));
}
```

