## 8. Animation & Transitions

### 8.1 Timing Functions

```css
--ease-out-expo: cubic-bezier(0.19, 1, 0.22, 1);
--ease-in-out: cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
--spring: cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
```

### 8.2 Durations

| Action | Duration | Easing |
|--------|----------|--------|
| Hover state | 150ms | ease-out |
| Panel open/close | 300ms | ease-out-expo |
| Zoom level change | 400ms | ease-in-out |
| Drag drop | 200ms | spring |
| Toast notification | 200ms in, 150ms out | ease-out |

### 8.3 LOD Transitions

When transitioning between LOD levels (heatmap -> bars -> capsules):

```
Duration: 300-500ms
Technique: Cross-fade with scale
- Outgoing: opacity 1->0, scale 1->0.95
- Incoming: opacity 0->1, scale 1.05->1
```

