## 11. Accessibility

### 11.1 Color Contrast

All text must meet WCAG 2.1 AA standards:
- Normal text: 4.5:1 contrast ratio minimum
- Large text (18px+): 3:1 contrast ratio minimum

### 11.2 Focus States

```css
:focus-visible {
  outline: 2px solid #1976D2;
  outline-offset: 2px;
}
```

### 11.3 Alternative Indicators

Never rely on color alone. Use:
- Icons alongside status colors
- Patterns (hatching) for conflicts
- Text labels for critical states

