## 13. Implementation Checklist

When implementing any UI component, verify:

- [ ] Colors match the design system palette
- [ ] Typography follows the type scale
- [ ] Spacing uses 4px/8px increments
- [ ] Border radius is consistent (4px for small, 8px for medium)
- [ ] Shadows follow the elevation system
- [ ] Hover/focus states are implemented
- [ ] Transitions are smooth (150-300ms)
- [ ] Responsive behavior is considered